{"tid":2135153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"董建華：充分理解和尊重政府決定押後立法會選舉","createTime":"2020-08-01T08:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T10:33:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9b200184265754ec27b320bffbec35c674537f57","tid":2135153,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541253-20200801.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541253-20200801.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=e3d79f1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541253-20200801.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=436203ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541253-20200801.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席、前行政長官董建華表示，充分理解和尊重政府押後立法會選舉的決定。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，押後立法會選舉是嚴肅的決定，相信特區政府經過深思熟慮、衡量各種因素後作出相關安排，並合理合法，相信社會各界支持特區政府的決定，並致力在疫情後，確保明年立法會選舉順利進行。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，特區政府有責任和義務，確保選舉在公平公正、安全有序的環境下進行。他提到，全球受到疫情影響，多個國家包括英國、意大利和澳洲，都宣布押後地方選舉；本港疫情未知何時見頂，認為各項大型活動均會影響市民大眾健康和安全。"},{"pid":"b1e161ec8d22e339fee86c506f93d56ca1bce754","tid":2135153,"uid":173207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"又係老懵董呢條老而不<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7237491efb673ff3a4684bb83409ebaf346723","tid":2135153,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"你死未啊"},{"pid":"a6e2ba20cfcf2f0e8f02abeed5ca16b633031b9d","tid":2135153,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">老懵董填命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" clas